<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期天早上，爷爷正在给每个人做薄饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊仍然穿着她的睡衣，在说养鸡的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这只鸡有一个蓝色的尾巴。”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，这只脚上有羽毛！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈笑了。“它们看起来像室内拖鞋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷拿给乔伊一盘薄饼，在她身后看了看目录。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看到那只有黑白条纹的了吗？”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我小时候有一只这样的母鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时它睡在我腿上，就像一只猫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸笑了。“那么乔伊！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们养些鸡怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊的眼睛睁得大大的，她的脸上露出了大大的笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，爸爸！我们可以吗？我们能买些小鸡吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们不会一直很小的。”妈妈提醒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们会变成大鸡。你会照顾它们吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你会喂它们吃的和水吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我保证。”乔伊说，“我也会捡鸡蛋的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以用那些新鲜鸡蛋做一些美味蛋卷。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂在哪儿？”乔伊问道，在桌子旁跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑到楼梯那里，喊道：“下来，凯蒂！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>楼上，凯蒂没有听见她姐姐的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她正忙着站在浴室的镜子前看自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪“杰利”坐在门口，舔着它的灰色的毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我动手啦。”凯蒂拿起剪刀低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰利停止舔毛，用圆圆的黄眼睛看着凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>楼下，爸爸在说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当我们自给自足时，这对地球有好处。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我还记得如何照顾小鸡。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你得教我，爷爷。”乔伊坐回桌边回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经放弃了努力吸引凯蒂的注意力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天我会把一本关于养鸡方面的书带回家。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在柳树溪图书馆兼职。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，大家都抬头看天花板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们听到凯蒂在上面走廊里的脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们听到她哐哐地跑下楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她来了。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家，早上好！”凯蒂蹦跳进厨房大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她光着脚转了一圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“注意到我有什么不同吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦古一直在角落里打盹。它睁开了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我注意到你拿着剪刀跑下来！”妈妈大声责怪道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那真的很危险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂低头看着手中的剪刀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀。”她说，“对不起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的头发好像有变化。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你剪了个刘海！”乔伊脱口而出。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“答对了！”凯蒂喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊皱起眉头。“可是，凯蒂。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们看起来不一样了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。”凯蒂高兴地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从现在开始，我就是那个有刘海的了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在桌旁坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷，能给我些薄饼吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你剪得不错，凯蒂。”妈妈评价道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看了一圈桌子，很不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是......我们看起来还像双胞胎吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。”凯蒂纠正道，“我们看起来完全不一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，妈妈开口了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊，告诉凯蒂小鸡的事情吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小鸡？”凯蒂重复道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”乔伊说，“我们要从‘咯咯农场’弄来小鸡！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂盯着乔伊。“我们要做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可多了。”乔伊又笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看，它们必须在室内住一段时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们必须给它们保暖，每分钟都要看着它们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当凯蒂想到可爱的小鸡时，她差点笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，她马上记起自己是多诺万双胞胎中不喜欢小鸡的那个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊注意到凯蒂茫然的表情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不激动吗？”她问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂耸了耸肩，把糖浆倒在薄饼上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最后一次吃薄饼的机会，姑娘们。”爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊和我得把厨房打扫干净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我们有一个养鸡计划！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>